  <brief_title>Prevention of IPH: Electric Warming Mattress vs Forced Air Warming Blanket</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study to Determine if Modern Under-patient Warming Mattresses Are as Effective as Forced-air Warming Blankets in Preventing Peri-operative Hypothermia</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Brighton and Sussex University Hospitals NHS Trust</agency>
